OL,5, A man who shot, stabbed and smothered  
OL,6, his young son to death has been found  
OL,7, guilty of murder.                      
OL,9,FLukasz Czapla, 41, killed two-year-old 
OL,10,FJuliusz after splitting up with the    
OL,11,Fboy's mother.                          
OL,13,FCzapla was given a life sentence and   
OL,14,Fthe judge said he would serve at least 
OL,15,F23 years before being eligible to apply
OL,16,Ffor parole.                            
OL,18,FHe had denied murdering the toddler in 
OL,19,Fhis home in Muirhouse, Edinburgh, in   
OL,20,FNovember 2020.                         
